event focusing on recent developments in: data intensive science for diverse areas of science; scalable
scientific algorithms; advanced software tools; computational grids; advanced numerical methods; and
novel application areas. ICCS2014 will also feature the important advances in computational science
towards exascale computing. ICCS includes work focusing on the application of computational
methods in diverse areas including, Computational Biology, Computational Finance, Earth Sciences,
Social Sciences and complex systems at large.
ICCS is well known for its excellent line up of keynote speakers and this year is no exception. The
keynotes for 2014 are:
